Where it says `// do stuff`, you need to do two things:

[1.] You need to add the JavaScript snippet like this:

    PdfWriter writer = stamper.getWriter();
    writer.addJavaScript(Utilities.readFileToString(RESOURCE));

[2.] You need to add some JavaScript to specific fields to call the custom methods you&#39;ve added.
In the example, you see a case where we add JavaScript as an additional action. You also see how we add a new button with a specific action. It&#39;s up to you to decide what is needed in your specific case.


